# ===== Generated artifacts (rebuilt in CI) =====
# Tailwind CSS is compiled by .github/workflows/pages.yml from
# docs/input.css + docs/tailwind.config.js. Keeping the compiled file
# out of VCS avoids binary churn in PR diffs.
docs/assets/tailwind.css

# ===== Temp helper scripts (ignored locally, not for reuse) =====
# Catch-all for scratch files that start with a single leading underscore
# (_msg.txt, _pins.json, _normalize.py, _upgrade_pins.ps1, ...). The
# `_[!_]` guard leaves Python dunder files such as __init__.py alone.
_[!_]*.py
_[!_]*.ps1
_[!_]*.json
_[!_]*.txt
_[!_]*.md
